  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/62fc3af1e4a1a9f0438f235d020bfb76.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Fireside is an uplifting narrative experience about a journey and the breaks that follow it. Make friends, trade and chat at the campfire, weave connections, and explore a serene magic-filled world.<br><br><strong>Connect With Fellow Travellers</strong><br>Your friends could always use your help! Chat with the folks you meet, learn their stories and while traveling on, be on the lookout for what your friends could need!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Collect And Trade</strong><br>On your journey, you’ll collect an array of supplies, trinkets, and other stuff you or your friends could use. Trade with others to get what you need for your next steps, and provide your allies with the means to carry on!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build Your Community</strong><br>Use the materials you find or trade to build and improve your home and invite your new pals to visit!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Serene, Non-Violent Experience</strong><br>Fireside will never want you to harm anyone. So kick back, make a cup of warm tea, turn up Fireside’s tranquil ambiance, and enjoy the calm of NOW.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/62fc3af1e4a1a9f0438f235d020bfb76.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Fireside is an uplifting narrative experience about a journey and the breaks that follow it. Make friends, trade and chat at the campfire, weave connections, and explore a serene magic-filled world.<br><br><strong>Connect With Fellow Travellers</strong><br>Your friends could always use your help! Chat with the folks you meet, learn their stories and while traveling on, be on the lookout for what your friends could need!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/ffc1d3e64498905f95548f9086d2fb45.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Collect And Trade</strong><br>On your journey, you’ll collect an array of supplies, trinkets, and other stuff you or your friends could use. Trade with others to get what you need for your next steps, and provide your allies with the means to carry on!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/be1aa872e48aa61754c38c5c0bb21db2.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build Your Community</strong><br>Use the materials you find or trade to build and improve your home and invite your new pals to visit!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/428f5d2a2d1703a0450e7887b281b30c.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Serene, Non-Violent Experience</strong><br>Fireside will never want you to harm anyone. So kick back, make a cup of warm tea, turn up Fireside’s tranquil ambiance, and enjoy the calm of NOW.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.poster.avif?t=1763466943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.webm?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1722700/extras/d4aaaa473c8de03078685c3c79b9572a.mp4?t=1763466943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
